{"id":248198,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-贵阳代贞祯看病劳教奇案，乌当区法院驳/","date":"2012-08-21T19:30:43Z","modified":"2012-08-21T19:30:43Z","title":"维权网 | 贵阳代贞祯看病劳教奇案，乌当区法院驳回起诉（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span>，贵州省开阳县金中镇沙坝村龙堰代贞祯收到贵阳市乌当区法院行政判决书。该判决书驳回代贞祯的诉讼请求，即请求法院确认贵阳市劳动教养委员会作出对代贞祯劳动教养的决定违法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>二○一○年五月六日上午，身体虚弱的代贞祯要去贵阳医院门诊看病，在开阳县客车站购买了当天开往贵阳的客车票，并上车待发。因该车上有访民，当地政府指使客车站不准发车。于是，政府工作人员与访民发生了冲突，导致其他的车辆也不能按时发车，乘客滞留车站。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当地政府如临大敌，出动防暴大队将代贞祯和访民高永强、代天娥、代证祥、丁润珍抓获。代贞祯被行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天，又被劳教</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>个月，即从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>代贞祯因外出看病被抓而劳教，堪称奇案。代贞祯仅仅是为了外出看病，当地政府误以为是上访，而将其先拘留后劳教，太冤。代贞祯劳教期满释放后，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>，用特快邮件向乌当法院递交了起诉材料和授权委托书，从此杳无音信。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，代贞祯到乌当法院查询立案情况。该院承认已经收到诉讼材料，但已经丢失，要求代贞祯再交一份起诉状。乌当法院随意丢失代贞祯的诉讼材料，恰恰说明该院缺乏责任心。其判决的要害是掩盖了“一事再罚”的违法性。代贞祯表示将提起上诉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uDNOexOuM70/UDO1PIn-8rI/AAAAAAAALuU/RUsSjgsEGgU/s1600/0.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uDNOexOuM70/UDO1PIn-8rI/AAAAAAAALuU/RUsSjgsEGgU/s320/0.jpg\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-LSsqgqHPNuw/UDO1XpiSkSI/AAAAAAAALuc/Eg_Dg4Js6QI/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-LSsqgqHPNuw/UDO1XpiSkSI/AAAAAAAALuc/Eg_Dg4Js6QI/s1600/1.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ib3HksLiClc/UDO1lghXQiI/AAAAAAAALuk/MDwS6PGa2Qo/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ib3HksLiClc/UDO1lghXQiI/AAAAAAAALuk/MDwS6PGa2Qo/s1600/2.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kWQR4i2_Eoc/UDO1usW9JWI/AAAAAAAALus/Gu_fr9gPg7g/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kWQR4i2_Eoc/UDO1usW9JWI/AAAAAAAALus/Gu_fr9gPg7g/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"225\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-uDFKCLFiRZo/UDO11GB3j5I/AAAAAAAALu0/XNIPg6twy2Y/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-uDFKCLFiRZo/UDO11GB3j5I/AAAAAAAALu0/XNIPg6twy2Y/s320/4.jpg\" width=\"230\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-9041931037924087968?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 